fields.content: Found this place down the street from our hotel. First time having currywurst and it was excellent!
Pretty cool burger place - seating both inside and outside.
Love the mini Prussians, the truffle cake is OUT of this world!
Super cozy cafe mixed with an interesting bookstore.
Service was good, very pleasant staff, but overall the meal was a let down, and very expensive.
it's worth a visit, and certainly if you're looking for something quick and inexpensive to eat
The place was very inviting, and it offered full kitchen service for longer with very nice staff
Das Essen war gut, jedoch nichts besonderes  und kostete 29,- CHF
Great location and bar, unfortunately one employee thinks she can load her crappy,  stressed out!
We ordered our food two hours ago. It still isn't here.
As a vegetarian, I very much appreciated the wide variety of proteins available
They used healthy ingredients and delicious seasonings. Loved every bite!
The setup is a bit of a mosh pit but I like the casualness of the whole place.
Excellent outside seating area, located in a calm neighborhood
you're watching your kids play in the fountain, enjoying a beer, ice cream, or dinner!
Great place for casual day drinks with friends on a nice day!
Cannot review because it was too crowded and we couldn't find a spot
Very good coffee including soy cappuccino!
Friendly staff. DELICIOUS espresso. Huge work space.
Food was good, not great to demand that kind of money.
Not so big, not too small.  Very casual outdoor seating
The restaurant is very cozy and nicely decorated.
Try evenings, they have live music events
Needless to say the front desk was hardly any help and my concerns fell on deaf ears !!
The staff was very pleasant and accommodating.
The accompanying cappuccino was also good although there are better options throughout the city.
Excellent lunch here with a very fine menu. Something for everyone.
The dinner here was also good, but a little bit on the pricy side
The restaurant was located on the first floor of the hotel and was very clean and pleasant.
dscadsc
Beautiful location and space, with very good service, but the food was OK in regards to the price.
The food was beautifully presented and tasted quite good, but the service was a bit slow.
Great service and reasonably priced menu.
the best ever review
Great atmosphere but poor service
The servers have no clue what they are doing so when it gets crowded
Fantastic decor, discrete service, fresh and tasty food makes this restaurant a must go to
the food is fresh but too spicy for little one!
Good coffees, freshly made sandwiches and a positive vibe.
